<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Cartotecnica — Calcolatore Faldoni</title>
<meta name="description" content="Calcolatore tecnico per la produzione di faldoni d'archivio. Misure, tagli, fabbisogno materiale.">
<meta property="og:title" content="Cartotecnica — Calcolatore Faldoni">
<meta property="og:description" content="App per calcolo misure, tagli e fabbisogno materiale nella produzione di faldoni archivio.">
<meta property="og:type" content="website">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,400;9..144,600;9..144,800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --ink:#1a1410;
    --paper:#f4ede0;
    --paper-2:#ebe1cc;
    --rule:#1a1410;
    --accent:#b8341a;
    --accent-soft:#d9a48a;
    --muted:#6b5d4a;
    --ok:#3a6b3a;
    --warn:#a86a1f;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  html,body{background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink);font-family:'Fraunces',Georgia,serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
  body{
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 12% 8%, rgba(184,52,26,0.04), transparent 40%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 88% 92%, rgba(26,20,16,0.05), transparent 50%);
    min-height:100vh;
  }
  .container{max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 24px 80px}
  @media (max-width:640px){.container{padding:20px 14px 60px}}

  header{
    border-bottom:2px solid var(--ink);
    padding-bottom:18px;
    margin-bottom:28px;
    display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:space-between;
    gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .brand{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px}
  .brand .eyebrow{
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);font-weight:500;
  }
  .brand h1{
    font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(28px,4.2vw,42px);
    line-height:1;letter-spacing:-0.02em;font-style:italic;
  }
  .brand h1 span{font-style:normal;font-weight:400}
  .header-meta{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);text-align:right;line-height:1.7}

  nav.tabs{
    display:flex;gap:0;margin-bottom:24px;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink);
    overflow-x:auto;scrollbar-width:none;
  }
  nav.tabs::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}
  .tab{
    background:transparent;border:none;cursor:pointer;
    padding:12px 18px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
    font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--muted);border-bottom:3px solid transparent;
    margin-bottom:-1px;white-space:nowrap;transition:all .15s;
  }
  .tab:hover{color:var(--ink)}
  .tab.active{color:var(--ink);border-bottom-color:var(--accent);font-weight:700}

  .panel{display:none;animation:fadeIn .25s ease}
  .panel.active{display:block}
  @keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(4px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}

  section.card{
    background:#fbf6ea;
    border:1px solid var(--ink);
    padding:22px 24px;
    margin-bottom:18px;
    position:relative;
  }
  section.card h2{
    font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:800;font-size:22px;
    margin-bottom:4px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;
  }
  section.card .sub{
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);
    text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.12em;margin-bottom:18px;
  }
  .section-num{
    position:absolute;top:-14px;left:18px;
    background:var(--ink);color:var(--paper);
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;
    padding:3px 8px;letter-spacing:.15em;font-weight:700;
  }

  .grid{display:grid;gap:14px}
  .grid-2{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
  .grid-3{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}
  .grid-4{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)}
  @media (max-width:780px){.grid-3,.grid-4{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}
  @media (max-width:480px){.grid-2,.grid-3,.grid-4{grid-template-columns:1fr}}

  .field{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}
  .field label{
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;
    text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--muted);font-weight:500;
  }
  .field .row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
  .field input[type=number]{
    width:100%;padding:9px 10px;
    background:var(--paper);border:1px solid var(--ink);
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;
    color:var(--ink);outline:none;
  }
  .field input[type=number]:focus{background:#fff;box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px var(--accent)}
  .field input[type=text]{
    width:100%;padding:9px 10px;background:var(--paper);
    border:1px solid var(--ink);font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:15px;outline:none;
  }
  .field .unit{
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);
    text-transform:uppercase;min-width:18px;
  }

  .derived{
    background:var(--paper-2);border:1px dashed var(--ink);
    padding:12px 14px;
  }
  .derived .label{
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;
    text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--muted);
  }
  .derived .val{
    font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:600;
    line-height:1.1;margin-top:2px;font-feature-settings:"tnum";
  }
  .derived .val small{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-weight:400;margin-left:4px}
  .derived .note{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:4px}

  .layout-wrap{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:18px;align-items:start}
  @media (max-width:780px){.layout-wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .layout-svg{
    background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--ink);padding:10px;
    aspect-ratio:102/72;width:100%;
  }
  .layout-info{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}

  .list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;border:1px solid var(--ink);background:#fbf6ea}
  .list .row{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;
    padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(26,20,16,.15);
    align-items:center;gap:10px;
  }
  .list .row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
  .list .row .k{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:15px}
  .list .row .k small{display:block;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-top:2px}
  .list .row .v{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;text-align:right;font-feature-settings:"tnum"}
  .list .row.total{background:var(--ink);color:var(--paper)}
  .list .row.total .k small{color:rgba(244,237,224,.65)}

  .tile{
    background:var(--ink);color:var(--paper);
    padding:18px 20px;border:1px solid var(--ink);
    display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;
  }
  .tile .l{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.14em;color:rgba(244,237,224,.7)}
  .tile .n{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:36px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;font-feature-settings:"tnum";font-style:italic}
  .tile .n span{font-style:normal;font-size:14px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:400;margin-left:6px;color:rgba(244,237,224,.7)}
  .tile .extra{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:rgba(244,237,224,.7);margin-top:4px}
  .tile.accent{background:var(--accent)}
  .tile.accent .l, .tile.accent .extra{color:rgba(244,237,224,.85)}

  .btn{
    background:var(--ink);color:var(--paper);border:1px solid var(--ink);
    padding:10px 18px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;
    letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;font-weight:600;
    transition:all .15s;
  }
  .btn:hover{background:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent)}
  .btn.ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--ink)}
  .btn.ghost:hover{background:var(--ink);color:var(--paper)}
  .btn.danger{background:transparent;color:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent)}
  .btn.danger:hover{background:var(--accent);color:var(--paper)}
  .btn-row{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:16px}

  .model-card{
    background:#fbf6ea;border:1px solid var(--ink);padding:14px 16px;
    display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:12px;
  }
  .model-card .info{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;flex:1;min-width:0}
  .model-card .info .name{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:600}
  .model-card .info .meta{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em}
  .model-card .actions{display:flex;gap:6px}
  .model-card .btn{padding:6px 12px;font-size:10px}

  @media print{
    nav.tabs, .no-print{display:none !important}
    .panel{display:block !important}
    body{background:#fff}
    section.card{break-inside:avoid;page-break-inside:avoid}
  }

  .footer{
    margin-top:40px;padding-top:18px;border-top:1px solid var(--ink);
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;
    color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.14em;
    display:flex;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;
  }

  .alert{
    background:#fef3e6;border-left:3px solid var(--warn);
    padding:10px 14px;font-size:13px;margin-top:10px;
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

  <header>
    <div class="brand">
      <div class="eyebrow">— Cartotecnica · Calcolatore tecnico —</div>
      <h1><span>Faldoni</span> &amp; archivio</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="header-meta no-print">
      Modello attivo:<br>
      <strong id="activeModelName" style="color:var(--ink);font-size:13px">— Standard —</strong>
    </div>
  </header>

  <nav class="tabs no-print" id="tabs">
    <button class="tab active" data-tab="misure">① Misure</button>
    <button class="tab" data-tab="layout">② Layout &amp; pezzi/foglio</button>
    <button class="tab" data-tab="produzione">③ Produzione</button>
    <button class="tab" data-tab="modelli">④ Modelli salvati</button>
  </nav>

  <div class="panel active" id="tab-misure">

    <section class="card">
      <div class="section-num">01 / CARTELLA</div>
      <h2>Misure base della cartella</h2>
      <p class="sub">Inserisci qui le misure di partenza. Tutto il resto si ricalcola da solo.</p>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="field">
          <label>Piatto — larghezza</label>
          <div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="piatto_l" value="28"><span class="unit">cm</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label>Piatto — altezza</label>
          <div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="piatto_h" value="38"><span class="unit">cm</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label>Dorso — larghezza</label>
          <div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="dorso_l" value="10"><span class="unit">cm</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <div class="section-num">02 / FORMATI MATERIE PRIME</div>
      <h2>Fogli, rotoli, bobine</h2>
      <p class="sub">Modifica se il fornitore cambia formato</p>
      <div class="grid grid-4">
        <div class="field"><label>Foglio cartone — L</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="foglio_cartone_l" value="102"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Foglio cartone — H</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="foglio_cartone_h" value="72"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Foglio carta — L</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="foglio_carta_l" value="102"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Foglio carta — H</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="foglio_carta_h" value="72"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Rotolo tela — altezza</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="tela_h" value="102"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Rotolo tela — lunghezza</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="tela_lung" value="50"><span class="unit">m</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Bobina fettuccia</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="1" id="fettuccia_bob" value="400"><span class="unit">m</span></div></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <div class="section-num">03 / COMPONENTI TELA</div>
      <h2>Misure dei pezzi in tela</h2>
      <p class="sub">Per ogni pezzo: dimensioni e quantità per cartella</p>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="field"><label>Dorso tela — L</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="dt_l" value="17"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Dorso tela — H</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="dt_h" value="40.5"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Q.tà per cartella</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="1" id="dt_q" value="1"><span class="unit">pz</span></div></div>

        <div class="field"><label>Patta piccola — L</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="pp_l" value="25.5"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Patta piccola — H</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="pp_h" value="28"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Q.tà per cartella</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="1" id="pp_q" value="2"><span class="unit">pz</span></div></div>

        <div class="field"><label>Patta grande — L</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="pg_l" value="25.5"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Patta grande — H</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="pg_h" value="38.5"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Q.tà per cartella</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="1" id="pg_q" value="1"><span class="unit">pz</span></div></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <div class="section-num">04 / COMPONENTI CARTA</div>
      <h2>Misure dei pezzi in carta</h2>
      <p class="sub">Rivestimenti esterni, interni, dorso e patte</p>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="field"><label>Piatto esterno — L</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="cpe_l" value="28.5"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Piatto esterno — H</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="cpe_h" value="42"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Q.tà per cartella</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="1" id="cpe_q" value="2"><span class="unit">pz</span></div></div>

        <div class="field"><label>Piatto interno — L</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="cpi_l" value="26.5"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Piatto interno — H</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="cpi_h" value="37.5"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Q.tà per cartella</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="1" id="cpi_q" value="2"><span class="unit">pz</span></div></div>

        <div class="field"><label>Dorso carta — L</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="cd_l" value="17"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Dorso carta — H</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="cd_h" value="37.5"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Q.tà per cartella</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="1" id="cd_q" value="1"><span class="unit">pz</span></div></div>

        <div class="field"><label>Carta patta piccola — L</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="cpp_l" value="23.5"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Carta patta piccola — H</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="cpp_h" value="26"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Q.tà per cartella</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="1" id="cpp_q" value="2"><span class="unit">pz</span></div></div>

        <div class="field"><label>Carta patta grande — L</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="cpg_l" value="23.5"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Carta patta grande — H</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="cpg_h" value="36"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Q.tà per cartella</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="1" id="cpg_q" value="1"><span class="unit">pz</span></div></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <div class="section-num">05 / FETTUCCIA</div>
      <h2>Lunghezze fettuccia per cartella</h2>
      <p class="sub">Quanti pezzi e di che lunghezza servono per ogni faldone</p>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="field"><label>Fettuccia dorso — pezzi</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="1" id="fd_q" value="1"><span class="unit">pz</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Fettuccia dorso — lunghezza</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="fd_l" value="11"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field derived" style="padding:6px 10px"><div class="label">Tot dorso/cartella</div><div class="val" id="fd_tot" style="font-size:18px">—</div></div>

        <div class="field"><label>Fettuccia cartella — pezzi</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="1" id="fc_q" value="6"><span class="unit">pz</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Fettuccia cartella — lunghezza</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="fc_l" value="28"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field derived" style="padding:6px 10px"><div class="label">Tot cartella/cartella</div><div class="val" id="fc_tot" style="font-size:18px">—</div></div>

        <div class="field"><label>Fettuccia patta piccola — pezzi</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="1" id="fp_q" value="2"><span class="unit">pz</span></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label>Fettuccia patta piccola — lunghezza</label><div class="row"><input type="number" step="0.1" id="fp_l" value="32"><span class="unit">cm</span></div></div>
        <div class="field derived" style="padding:6px 10px"><div class="label">Tot patta/cartella</div><div class="val" id="fp_tot" style="font-size:18px">—</div></div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>

  <div class="panel" id="tab-layout">

    <section class="card">
      <div class="section-num">CARTONE — FOGLIO 102 × 72</div>
      <h2>Disposizione su foglio di cartone</h2>
      <p class="sub">Calcolo automatico: piatti e dorsi affiancati sul foglio</p>
      <div class="layout-wrap">
        <svg class="layout-svg" id="svg_cartone" viewBox="0 0 102 72" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet"></svg>
        <div class="layout-info" id="info_cartone"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <div class="section-num">TELA — FASCE DA ROTOLO</div>
      <h2>Tagli dalla tela</h2>
      <p class="sub">Tre tipi di fascia: dorso, patte piccole, patte grandi</p>

      <div class="layout-wrap" style="margin-bottom:20px">
        <svg class="layout-svg" id="svg_tela_dt" viewBox="0 0 102 50" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" style="aspect-ratio:auto;height:140px"></svg>
        <div class="layout-info" id="info_tela_dt"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="layout-wrap" style="margin-bottom:20px">
        <svg class="layout-svg" id="svg_tela_pp" viewBox="0 0 102 50" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" style="aspect-ratio:auto;height:140px"></svg>
        <div class="layout-info" id="info_tela_pp"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="layout-wrap">
        <svg class="layout-svg" id="svg_tela_pg" viewBox="0 0 102 50" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" style="aspect-ratio:auto;height:140px"></svg>
        <div class="layout-info" id="info_tela_pg"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <div class="section-num">CARTA — FOGLIO 102 × 72</div>
      <h2>Disposizione carta sul foglio</h2>
      <p class="sub">Pezzi per foglio per ogni tipologia di rivestimento</p>

      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Fraunces';font-weight:600;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">Piatti esterni</h3>
          <svg class="layout-svg" id="svg_carta_pe" viewBox="0 0 102 72"></svg>
          <div class="layout-info" id="info_carta_pe" style="margin-top:10px"></div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Fraunces';font-weight:600;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">Piatti interni</h3>
